<li id="cite_note-65"><b><a href="#cite_ref-65" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.cesnur.org/testi/guyard_en.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.cesnur.org/testi/guyard_en.htm" rel="nofollow">"Guyard Guilty of Defamation"</a>. Cesnur. <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2000-03-23"><a href="/wiki/2000" title="2000">2000</a>-<a href="/wiki/March_23" title="March 23">03-23</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cesnur.org/testi/guyard_en.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.cesnur.org/testi/guyard_en.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.cesnur.org/testi/guyard_en.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-11-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Guyard+Guilty+of+Defamation&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2000-03-23%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=Cesnur&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cesnur.org%2Ftesti%2Fguyard_en.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Anthroposophy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
