<li>Archiati, Pietro, <i>Reincarnation in Modern Life: Toward a New Christian Awareness</i>. Temple Lodge Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0904693880" class="internal">ISBN 0-904693-88-0</a></li>
