<li>Edelglass, Stephen et al., <i>The Marriage of Sense and Thought</i>, Lindisfarne Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0940262827" class="internal">ISBN 0-940262-82-7</a></li>
<li>Forward, William and Blaxland-de Lange, Simon (eds.), <i>Trumpet to the Morn</i> (Golden Blade 2001), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0953160033" class="internal">ISBN 0-9531600-3-3</a></li>
