<li>Gulbekian, Sevak (ed.), <i>The Future is Now: Anthroposophy at the New Millennium</i>, Temple Lodge Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1902636090" class="internal">ISBN 1-902636-09-0</a></li>
<li>Hauschka, Rudolf, <i>At the Dawn of a New Age</i>, Anthroposophic Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0919924255" class="internal">ISBN 0-919924-25-5</a></li>
<li>Hindes, James H. (1995) <i>Renewing Christianity</i> Floris Books</li>
<li>Klocek, Dennis, <i>The Seer's Handbook: A Guide to Higher Perception</i>, SteinerBooks 2006. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0880105488" class="internal">ISBN 0-88010-548-8</a></li>
