<li>Lievegoed, Bernard, <i>The Battle for the Soul: The Working Together of Three Great Leaders of Humanity</i>, Hawthorn Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1869890647" class="internal">ISBN 1-869890-64-7</a></li>
