<li>Murphy, Christine (ed.), <i>Iscador: Mistletoe and Cancer Therapy</i>. Lantern Books, 2005. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/193005176X" class="internal">ISBN 1-930051-76-X</a></li>
<li>Nesfield-Cookson, Bernard, <i>Michael and the Two-Horned Beast: The Challenge of Evil Today in the Light of Rudolf Steiner's Science of the Spirit</i>, Temple Lodge Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0904693988" class="internal">ISBN 0-904693-98-8</a></li>
